phpfoxLABS - MegaPoke phpFox Module Instillation Guide

IMPORTANT: Please follow all steps in this installation guide in order to make this plugin worksmoothly.

I. SYSTEM REQUIREMENT:1. phpFox >= 2.0


II. TO UPGRADE (ALREADY INSTALLED) TO LATEST COPY:
1. Go to adminCP > extensions > product > manage product 
	a. next to phpfoxLABS MegaPoke click the "down arrow"
	b. in the drop down list that appears select "delete"

2. Follow the INSTALLATION steps below.


III. INSTALLATION:
1. Upload "upload" folder to phpFox root directory.

2. Go to adminCP > extensions > product > import product , install phpfoxLABS - MegaPokepackage.

3. Go to the Drop Down Menu in Admin Page: Modules > MegaPoke > Poke Types

4. Enter as many Poke Types as you want.

5. Go to a user Profile (other than yours) to see if MegaPoke is there, happy Poking. 


IV. EXTRA STUFF
1. In the "Phrase Manager" you can edit all the MegaPoke Phrases.   
2. In the "User Group Manager" you can set which user groups get access to MegaPoke.  2. In the "User Group Manager" you can turn off pokes showing in pokers news feed.

If you like this module, please checkout more at: http://phpfoxlabs.com/


